description: Record to support submission of GeneRIFs for a gene not in Gene (Bacterium cichorii; Bacterium formosanum; Chlorobacter cichorii; Phytomonas cichorii; Pseudomonas endiviae; Pseudomonas papaveris; probable synonym: "Pseudomonas papaveris" Lelliott and Wallace 1955.  Use when strain, subtype, isolate, etc. is unspecified, or when different from all specified ones in Gene.).
